OL,3,CMeet the man who ran 52 marathons in
OL,4,C52 weeks
OL,6,FA man from Lichfield has finished the
OL,7,Fmammoth task of running a marathon
OL,8,Fevery week for a year to raise money
OL,9,Ffor his local children's hospital.
OL,11,FChris Caddy has so far raised over
OL,12,F#5,000 for Birmingham Children's
OL,13,FHospital and run 1,326 miles.
OL,15,FHe's due to start his 52nd marathon at
OL,16,FBeacon Park on Saturday 16th August,
OL,17,Fat around 11am.
