OL,3,CMeet the man who ran 52 marathons in
OL,4,C52 weeks
OL,6,FHe told ITV News Central he was
OL,7,Fmotivated to take on the challenge
OL,8,Fwhen he was thinking about his
OL,9,Fdaughter, saying: "I've known quite a
OL,10,Ffew friends who've had children in the
OL,11,Fhospital, lots of friends who work
OL,12,Fthere"
OL,14,F"I've got a seven-year-old daughter
OL,15,Fmyself, and the pain I feel when she's
OL,16,Fill, even with minor illness, I can't
OL,17,Fcomprehend how families with children
OL,18,Fin the hospital must feel.
