OL,3,CMeet the man who ran 52 marathons in
OL,4,C52 weeks
OL,6,F"I want to inspire her that even if
OL,7,Fthings are hard, you can do them if
OL,8,Fyou put your mind to it."
OL,10,FHe said he's had to dig deep at times
OL,11,Fto finish the runs, adding: "I did one
OL,12,Fon New Year's Eve. I started late at
OL,13,Fnight. There had been a storm going
OL,14,Fon, and it was raining, and I'd been
OL,15,Fat work all day.
OL,17,F"There was no one about, just cabs and
OL,18,Fkabab shops. All I wanted was my bed
OL,19,Fand a bit of warmth that day."
