OL,3,CMeet the man who ran 52 marathons in
OL,4,C52 weeks
OL,6,F"I wanted to see if I could do it for
OL,7,Fa whole year. I wasn't sure it's
OL,8,Fsomething I'd be able to achieve."
OL,10,F"I had no idea how my body would
OL,11,Freact."
OL,13,F"When times get hard, you think of the
OL,14,Fcause you support. I think about my
OL,15,Fdaughter. No matter how hard it gets,
OL,16,Fyou remember the reason you're doing
OL,17,Fit and you keep going forward.
