OL,3,CMeet the man who ran 52 marathons in
OL,4,C52 weeks
OL,6,F"I'm accountable for my daughter now,
OL,7,Fso I can't give up. If she knows her
OL,8,FDad's given up, that defeats the
OL,9,Fpoint."
OL,11,FSam will cross the finish line of his
OL,12,Fchallenge in his home city of
OL,13,FLichfield.
OL,15,FCommenting that it might be an
OL,16,Femotional finish, he said: "I'll try
OL,17,Fnot to cry, I think. I go on holiday
OL,18,Fstraight after getting on the line, so
OL,19,Fthat will be nice."
